e is a tension between early and late cosmological\nmeasurements. As an appendix, we discuss the model building challenges of the\nuse of photon-axion conversion to make type Ia supernovae brighter to alleviate\nthe Hubble problem/crisis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Nov 2020 19:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 8 Dec 2020 15:40:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 15 Feb 2022 17:21:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-16"}
