f a defect line between the\ngravitational and non-gravitational regions. The gravity model is then\nholographically dual to an ensemble of boundary conditions in an open/closed\nTQFT without gravity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Nov 2020 00:46:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 2 Jul 2021 21:42:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-08"}
