lly, we recover earlier\napproximate dispersion relations that focus on low-frequency limits and make\ndirect correspondences with some selected kinetic theory results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Nov 2020 09:50:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-18"}
