ization with a specific task expertise. Implications for\nthe real time monitoring of grip forces and performance training in complex\ntask user systems are brought forward.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Nov 2020 15:50:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-13"}
